---
title: Rosemary-Walnut Crusted Chicken with Roasted Potatoes & Mixed Green Salad
description: We love the crispy crunchy topping on this delicious chicken. Fragrant rosemary and the deeply flavoured oils from the walnuts compliment tender chicken breast. We kept it classic with roasted potatoes and a lightly dressed salad.
